  m_text: "Let\u2019s share the cupcakes!\n\nMia: \u201CI\u2019m really hungry. I
    want about 1/2 of the cupcakes.\u201D\n\nLeo: \u201CI only need a small part.\u201D\n\nCecilia:
    \u201CI\u2019ll have the same as Leo.\u201D\n\nRemember to keep a share for yourself
    too!\n\nThink about the whole group before you share.\n\nPress F to check your
    answer."
